            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="luxury-card p-10 text-center group hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-500" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="0">
                <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-luxury-primary to-luxury-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-xl luxury-float">
                    <i class="fas fa-bolt text-3xl text-white"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 luxury-heading group-hover:text-luxury-primary transition-colors">Swift Response</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">I respond to all luxury inquiries within 6 hours with personalized attention and care</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="luxury-card p-10 text-center group hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-500" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-luxury-primary to-luxury-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-xl luxury-float">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-3xl text-white"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 luxury-heading group-hover:text-luxury-primary transition-colors">Ultimate Discretion</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Absolute confidentiality and the highest level of privacy in all communications</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="luxury-card p-10 text-center group hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-500" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-luxury-primary to-luxury-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-xl luxury-float">
                    <i class="fas fa-concierge-bell text-3xl text-white"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 luxury-heading group-hover:text-luxury-primary transition-colors">VIP Treatment</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Every interaction is handled with the utmost professionalism and luxury service standards</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

